statements: SELECT * FROM voter_registration_data;
SELECT voter_name, voter_age FROM voter_registration_data;
SELECT voter_name FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_age > 30;
SELECT * FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_gender = 'M';
SELECT voter_id, voter_name, registration_date FROM voter_registration_data ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT voter_name, voter_gender, registration_date, voter_age FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_age >= 18 ORDER BY registration_date DESC
SELECT * FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_gender = 'M' AND voter_age >= 21 ORDER BY voter_name ASC
SELECT voter_name, voter_gender, voter_age FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_name LIKE '%John%' OR voter_name LIKE '%Doe%' ORDER BY voter_name ASC, registration_date DESC
SELECT voter_name, voter_age FROM voter_registration_data WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01' ORDER BY registration_date DESC
SELECT voter_name, voter_gender FROM voter_registration_data WHERE voter_age >= 25 ORDER BY voter_gender ASC, voter_name DESC
SELECT * FROM voter_demographics;
SELECT voter_name, voter_party_affiliation FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_age > 30;
SELECT voter_name, voter_address FROM voter_demographics ORDER BY voter_name DESC;
SELECT voter_name, election_year FROM voter_demographics JOIN voting_history ON voter_demographics.voter_id = voting_history.voter_id;
SELECT voter_name, vote_cast FROM voter_demographics JOIN voting_history ON voter_demographics.voter_id = voting_history.voter_id WHERE vote_cast = 'Yes';
SELECT voter_name, voter_age, voter_party_affiliation FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_age > 30 ORDER BY voter_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM voting_history WHERE vote_cast = 'Yes' AND election_year = 2020;

SELECT voter_name, voter_age, voter_party_affiliation, election_year, vote_cast FROM voter_demographics INNER JOIN voting_history ON voter_demographics.voter_id = voting_history.voter_id WHERE voter_age BETWEEN 25 AND 40;
SELECT voter_name, voter_party_affiliation FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_party_affiliation IN ('Democrat', 'Republican') ORDER BY voter_party_affiliation ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT voter_party_affiliation FROM voter_demographics ORDER BY voter_party_affiliation ASC;
SELECT * FROM voter_demographics;
SELECT voter_name, voter_age FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_age > 30;
SELECT voter_id, registration_date FROM voter_demographics ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM voter_address WHERE state = 'NY';
SELECT voter_id, preferred_political_party FROM voter_preferences;
SELECT * FROM voter_demographics WHERE voter_age > 30;
SELECT voter_name, voter_gender FROM voter_demographics WHERE registration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT voter_name, street_address, city, state FROM voter_demographics INNER JOIN voter_address ON voter_demographics.voter_id = voter_address.voter_id;

SELECT voter_preferences.preferred_political_party, voter_demographics.voter_name FROM voter_preferences INNER JOIN voter_demographics ON voter_preferences.voter_id = voter_demographics.voter_id WHERE voter_preferences.voting_frequency = 'Regular';

SELECT voter_id, voter_name, voter_age, preferred_voting_method FROM voter_demographics LEFT JOIN voter_preferences ON voter_demographics.voter_id = voter_preferences.voter_id WHERE preferred_voting_method IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM VoterDemographics
SELECT first_name, last_name, age, gender FROM VoterDemographics WHERE age > 30
SELECT district_name, total_voters FROM VotingDistricts ORDER BY total_voters DESC
SELECT candidate_name, votes_received, vote_percentage FROM ElectionResults WHERE votes_received > 1000 ORDER BY vote_percentage DESC
SELECT registration_status, registration_date FROM VoterHistory WHERE registration_status='active'
SELECT * FROM VoterDemographics ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT first_name, age, gender FROM VoterDemographics WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT district_name, total_voters, male_voters, female_voters FROM VotingDistricts WHERE total_voters > 1000 ORDER BY total_voters DESC;
SELECT candidate_name, votes_received, vote_percentage FROM ElectionResults WHERE votes_received > 5000 ORDER BY vote_percentage DESC;
SELECT vh.registration_status, vh.registration_date, vd.district_name FROM VoterHistory vh JOIN VotingDistricts vd ON vh.voter_id = vd.id;
SELECT * FROM Voter;
SELECT first_name, last_name, age FROM Voter ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT voter_id, first_name, last_name, registration_date FROM Voter WHERE age > 30;
SELECT V.first_name, V.last_name, VA.party_name FROM Voter V LEFT JOIN VoterPartyAffiliation VA ON V.voter_id = VA.voter_id;
SELECT V.first_name, V.last_name, VD.district_name FROM Voter V INNER JOIN VoterDistrict VD ON V.voter_id = VD.district_id;
SELECT * FROM Voter;
SELECT first_name, last_name, age FROM Voter ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, v.age, vh.election_date FROM Voter v JOIN VotingHistory vh ON v.voter_id = vh.voter_id WHERE vh.vote_cast = TRUE;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, va.party_name FROM Voter v JOIN VoterPartyAffiliation va ON v.voter_id = va.voter_id WHERE va.affiliation_date >= '2021-01-01';
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, vd.district_name, vd.region FROM Voter v JOIN VoterDistrict vd ON v.voter_id = vd.district_id WHERE vd.region = 'East';
